		<hr size="1">I am a lvl 8 SK and all I hear are complaints about how difficult they are to play.  I personally enjoy the dificulties.  The whole purpose of the game is to roleplay your character.  Tanking everything in sight is just boring.  I made a wise choice early on and boutgh a bow.  My archery helps when some low level attacks me and then "TRIES" to run.  I get spells next level.  Everyone keeps saying SK spells suck.  Well if you wanted to be a Necro....  Personally I believe the spells are another of our many tools.  We must enjoy the SK for what it is.  Roleplay. Don't just sit there and keep saying man I wish I were lvl XX.  You'll get there.  Slower than most, but you'll enjoy the game more and appreciate your SK.  Dark Elves rule if you're going to play the way you should.<P>May the sons and daughters of Innoruuk Rule the Realm.<P><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
	</font>
