		<hr size="1">This is to the lvl 45. 1. 45th "circle" doesn't exist... for anyone. That would be the 45th lvl you get spells.( a small matter of semantics i know  but still annoying) 2. Most warrios at high lvls Use 2HS (until they add better 1HS) and we can wear armor roughly equivilent to them. True they have more hps, and the gap widens per lvl, and they get crits, but we make up for these inconsistences with our spells and smart playing. There is no trully smart plaing for a warrior. Semi intelligent playing maybe but smart playing no. they have to know when to pull when to step back when to request heals etc. We on the other and are far more self sufficient. I often get knocked by necros who say things like oh that spell i got it at lvl 8, and other things like that. Judging spells value on strict lvl basis is meaningless. Lvl 4 necro spells aren't always resisted by high lvl even cons, and even the first in the line of darkness and fear spells are very nice tools at high lvls. also certain spells scream this was meant for SK's but we gave it to necros so the evolution makes sense. Spells like vampiric embrace are a shinig example. As a troll SK i often team up with just a warrior as this is what most of my friends are. With this spell i significantly reduce down time by giving my hps to the warrior who doesn't get health back nearly as fast. Another example is disease cloud. Many people have talked about this spells useful ness in pvp environments to halt regen. An important use of this spell for SKs is taunting, place this very fast spell between attacks taunts and slams always gets that mobs attention, casters will thank you for it. We are a very powerful high lvl class. We are also a powerful midlvl class if you play it right.<BR>Thanks<BR>Beureguard <br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
